LINE.Text: Strength. Speed. A Thirst For Vengeance-The Giant Anaconda
Anacondas are large, non-venomous boas found in tropical South
America. However it was the 1997 movie 'Anaconda' that took an
investigative look at the extraordinary capabilities of the notoriously
elusive Giant Anaconda Unlike their smaller cousins, The Giant
Anaconda is no ordinary snake. Aside from its obvious larger size, it
possesses an impressive arsenal of deadly physical abilities.
